## Unit Test 規範

### 命名

```ts
describe('SubmitReviewUseCase', () => {
  it('should reject review shorter than 10 characters', async () => { ... });
  it('should emit ReviewSubmittedEvent on success', async () => { ... });
  it('should rollback on chain submission failure', async () => { ... });
});
```

### Arrange-Act-Assert

```ts
it('should submit a review', async () => {
  // Arrange
  const mockRepo = mock<IReviewRepository>();
  const useCase = new SubmitReviewUseCase(mockRepo);
  const input = { brokerId: '...', body: '...' };

  // Act
  const result = await useCase.execute(input);

  // Assert
  expect(result.success).toBe(true);
  expect(mockRepo.save).toHaveBeenCalledOnce();
});
```

### 獨立性

- ❌ 測試之間共用 state
- ❌ 測試依賴執行順序
- ❌ 測試直接連真實 DB / API
- ✅ 每個測試自己 setup / teardown

