## Solidity Test (Foundry)

詳見 `41-solidity-contracts.mdc`。重點：

- 必跑 unit + integration + invariant + fuzz
- 命名：`test_FunctionName_Condition_ExpectedBehavior`
- 用 `vm.expectRevert(CustomError.selector)` 而非字串

```solidity
function test_SubmitReview_AsUnverifiedUser_Reverts() public {
    address user = makeAddr("user");
    vm.prank(user);
    vm.expectRevert(IReviewRegistry.NotVerified.selector);
    registry.submitReview(brokerId, "0x...", "ipfs://...");
}
```

